---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="子迂的蠹酸齋">
    <main class="min-h-screen bg-void-black text-stucco-white font-sans pb-24">
  
        <div class="w-full !h-32 bg-[#1a1a1a] concrete-grid relative border-b border-white/10" >
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-void-black/80 to-transparent">這裡放首頁圖</div>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6">
          
          <div class="relative -mt-16 mb-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-end gap-6">
            
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-primary border-[6px] border-void-black shadow-xl shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-white font-black text-xs uppercase">Profile</span>
            </div>
          
            <div class="flex-1">
              
              <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-1">子迂的蠢酸齋</h1>
              
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-400 text-sm">
                <span class="font-medium">424 followers</span>
                <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-slate-600 rounded-full"></span>
                <span class="font-medium text-primary">1 software engineer</span>
              </div>
            
            </div>
            
            <button class="bg-[#222] text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-primary transition-all self-center md:self-end">
              Follow
            </button>
          
          </div>

          <nav class="flex gap-10 border-y border-white/5 py-4 mb-16 overflow-x-auto no-scrollbar">
            
            {['Coding', 'Finance', 'Design', 'Kaohsiung', 'Life'].map(item => (
              <a href="#" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-400 hover:text-primary tracking-wide transition-colors uppercase">{item}</a>
            ))}
    
          </nav>

          <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-24 items-center group cursor-pointer">
            
            <div class="aspect-[16/10] bg-[#151515] border border-white/10 overflow-hidden relative">
              
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-800 font-black text-4xl uppercase tracking-tighter opacity-20">Featured</div>
            
            </div>
      
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
              <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.2] text-white group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                房價、藝術品、單價、坪數：<br/>軟體視角下的數據觀察
              </h2>
        
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">        
                活到一把歲數，我們習慣把牆當成理所當然的東西，直到你開始用 SQL 結構化這些數據，你會發現每一塊磚頭都有它的邏輯位址...
              </p>
        
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">   
                <span>Yoshua</span> <span class="text-primary">·</span> <span>1d ago</span> <span class="text-primary">·</span> <span>5 min read</span>
              </div>     
            </div> 
          
          </section>

    
          <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10"> 
            {[1, 2, 3].map(i => (
              <div class="group cursor-pointer">
                
                <div class="aspect-video bg-[#111] border border-white/10 mb-6 relative">
                  
                  <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-800 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest opacity-30">Image {i}</div>
                </div>
          
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white leading-snug group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                  《建築詩篇與程式碼的交響》：<br/>柯比意教我的模矩化設計
                </h4>
              
              </div>
            ))}
          </section>

      </div>
    </main>
</Layout>